metadata.name: Woman #1
metadata.description: Sometimes events happen that are bigger than NFTs and the space that we’re all familiar with. We are not above being vocal about things that have transpired in the US of late… the bottomline is simple: we have no roadmap. We want to spread awareness and give back to 501(c)(3) that support women’s rights. [godhateswomenft.com](https://godhateswomenft.com/) to find out more.
